232
00:14:39,515 --> 00:14:41,475
Yong-sik!

233
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:43,227
Itu namamu?

234
00:14:43,310 --> 00:14:46,313
Ya, aku Hwang Yong-sik dari Polsek Ongsan.

235
00:14:46,397 --> 00:14:47,690
Omong-omong,

236
00:14:47,773 --> 00:14:49,400
rekaman dari tanggal 24...

237
00:14:49,483 --> 00:14:51,694
Yong-sik, kami pikir

238
