244
00:15:17,928 --> 00:15:19,054
Yeong-sim.

245
00:15:22,015 --> 00:15:23,267
<i>Pergi ke ladang bawang putih Yeong-sim.</i>

246
00:15:23,350 --> 00:15:25,602
Kenapa aku harus pedulikan
anjing melahirkan?

247
00:15:26,437 --> 00:15:27,646
Yeong-sim sialan.

248
00:15:27,730 --> 00:15:31,150
