273
00:16:48,185 --> 00:16:50,145
Bibi tertuaku punya putra

274
00:16:50,479 --> 00:16:52,231
yang juga bercerai.

275
00:16:52,314 --> 00:16:54,316
Dia tak punya anak dan seorang akuntan.

276
00:16:55,442 --> 00:16:56,985
Mungkin kalian berdua bisa...

277
00:16:59,530 --> 00:17:02,783
Sayang, aku butuh konsultasi.

278
00:17:06,995 --> 00:17:10,082
Ya, aku hanya... Kau tahu...

279
00:17:14,419 --> 00:17:17,464
- Apa?
