442
00:26:28,014 --> 00:26:30,100
Kenapa kau coba menyerahkan diri sekarang?

443
00:26:32,519 --> 00:26:34,562
Maksudku, ini...

444
00:26:35,772 --> 00:26:36,981
Begini...

